                <h1>Types of Apps Not Protected by Copyright</h1>
                <p>Not all apps are protected by copyright. For example, apps that solely consist of facts or ideas without creative expression—like simple utility tools or apps presenting raw data—aren't copyrightable. However, the unique design, code, and original content of an app are protected. Understanding these distinctions is crucial for developers.</p>
